strings: <voice_0x01001D03><se_high>Media princess: ...do you think i'm brown? ..not like that. Unfortunately, the capabilities do not affect us.
<voice_0x01001D04><se_high>Media princess: At first I thought that the dark world was just a dark void. But now I know that I was wrong, but there is no color.
<voice_0x01001D05><se_high>Media princess: I find it a bit sad... Do the people who live here see our world as colorful and bright.
<voice_0x01001D06><se_high>Media princess: I must admit there is something romantic about this desolate landscape, but I wouldn't stay there forever.
<voice_0x01001D07><se_high>Media princess: I mean... it can be a bit scary when it's dark.
<voice_0x01001D08><se_high>Media princess: But as long as I have you by my side, I know there is nothing to be afraid of.
